# NestJS Backend Rules

- Module structure: controller → service → repository
- DTOs in `dto/` with class-validator + Swagger decorators
- Prisma models in `prisma/schema.prisma` only — never in packages/shared
- Services map entities to shared response types; strip passwordHash and secrets
- Register new modules in `app.module.ts`
- Copy patterns from `docs/patterns/crud-feature/` and `_example` module
- Add unit tests in `__tests__/` alongside services
